{"tid":498972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【訪華第一戰】韓記者被踢臉鼻血狂流 目擊者爆衝突過程","createTime":"2017-12-14T10:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T14:02:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"381cf3bb7a6a734beee6e3b00491dbb662694083","tid":498972,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171214/large/1513243768_8779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171214%2Flarge%2F1513243768_8779.jpg&h=16595a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓總統文在寅訪華之旅，未見成果，便爆發了「第一戰」！2名隨文在寅團隊採訪的韓國攝影記者，今日遭到中方警衞阻攔採訪，還被毆傷送院，事件引發青瓦台關注，並隨即通過外交部向中方提出抗議。有韓媒引媒目擊者還原事發經過。<br />\n<br />\n據《Korean Times》報道，目擊者指，事發於今日上午10時56分左右，當時文在寅正北京國家會議中心出席中韓經貿合作交流會，參觀完韓國公司的展台後，移步前往另一展場。但文與其保安離開後，14名隨行的韓國記者及攝影記者卻被中國警衞阻攔。韓記者會表示他們需要跟隨文作報道，該些中國警衞卻揪着其中一名攝影記者Koh Young-kwon的衣領，將他推倒在地。Koh有一陣子無法站起來，另一名攝影記者欲拍下現場情況，卻被奪去相機。<br />\n<br />\n在短暫衝突後，韓國記者們終於被允許前往第二展場，但又被另外15名中國警衞阻止進入，記者們展示了記者證後仍不果。此時，另一名攝影記者Lee Chung-woo提出抗議，結果被那些警衞拉到一旁，並用拳頭圍毆，Lee倒地時，被其中一名警衞踢中臉。目擊者稱，韓方官員試圖阻止警衞們的暴力行為，但對方沒有理會。<br />\n<br />\n雖然當時韓方大部份保安都已隨文在寅離開，但仍有十多人出手阻止。兩名受傷的攝影記者隨後被送住文下榻的釣魚臺國賓館，由文的醫療團隊進行急救。目擊者透露，Koh的背部疼痛，Lee的雙眼則被打腫，還流鼻血，感到頭暈及想嘔，他隨後被送院接受電腦掃描及磁力共振檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171214/57581430\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57581430&d=VgOsMrzToc1whm0geNSfc0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2a11e133\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57581430&h=c6e4f098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171214/57581430</a>"},{"pid":"a658f288433096d27146d45f925cfe5fef33fff9","tid":498972,"uid":29874,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:06:23.000Z","msg":"中韓友好換來咪就係拳打腳踢，有咩問題啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 韓方未富先驕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b2bf52213a4f92bd6956c7cfbeba1297d82f6e","tid":498972,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那"},{"pid":"2c366a7b41fb6ccf0ac8029adf25b869f5958a2c","tid":498972,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"文在寅抵北京發表演說：中韓為生命共同體"},{"pid":"2ec54959d487164b0d3d9fc68980d46a14b486b2","tid":498972,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文在寅抵北京發表演說：中韓為生命共同體</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44817ddb7be9e259846cee3672d286a4a7d6a20","tid":498972,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>文在寅抵北京發表演說：中韓為生命共同體</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n扺撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c10902ac5772925aeea9fd0d63f80086304543","tid":498972,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:12:00.000Z","msg":"攪大佢"},{"pid":"d94d864405870c936091c41e5e34a1fb25f8383b","tid":498972,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>文在寅抵北京發表演說：中韓為生命共同體</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打在泡身，痛在支心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as